public HttpUtils.Request addEndpointPath(String endpoint)

Add a path to the endpoint Uri

Parameters:
    endpoint – String: Path to be added to the endpoint

Returns:
    Request: The current request with the added endpoint path

Example: 
request.setEndpoint('https://www.example-service.com/');
request.addEndpointPath('/api/v1/resource/');
System.debug(request.getUrl()); // Output => https://www.example-service.com/api/v1/resource/
